data.description: Multiple Offers Recieved- Highest and Best due by 2/11/24 at 10pm. Welcome to 2949 Bullard, where modern updates meet serene privacy on a lush .69 acre lot. This turn-key, 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers an impressive 2,012 sq ft of above-grade living space, complemented by a 572 sq ft unfinished basement ready for your personal touch. As you step inside, the open floor plan seamlessly connects the living areas, featuring rich wood floors throughout and an abundance of natural light. The updated kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting a sleek granite island that overlooks the dining area and convenient coffee bar. On the upper level you will find 3 spacious bedrooms and a full bath. In the lower level you'll be greeted by a quaint living room centered around a fireplace. Adjacent to living room is a bright bonus room offering flexible space for an office or playroom. An additional bedroom and full bathroom complete the lower level. From there step down into the 572 foot basement and you'll find an additional recreation area as well as laundry. Entertaining is a breeze with the spacious deck overlooking the expansive backyard, a private oasis with mature trees perfect for summer barbecues, fall bonfires, or simply enjoying the tranquil surroundings. The cherry on top is this property includes a 2-car attached garage, plus an additional 2-car detached garage built-in bar area and golf simulator. Roughly 2 miles from 59 and 23 make this homes location ideal for modern conveniences. 2949 Bullard has been well taken care of and is ready for it's new owner and all of the memories to be made.
